text: Highway Star may refer to: *"Highway Star" (song), a song on Deep Purple's 1972 album Machine Head *Highway Star, the band that became Stiff Little Fingers *Highway Star (manga), a 1979 graphic novel by Katsuhiro Otomo *Highway Star (film) *Highway Star, a Stand featured in Diamond is Unbreakable named after the Deep Purple song *Highway Star or Rad Racer, a 1987 NES video game by Square *Highway Star is car model brand name of Nissan
